Description: This app simulates time series data with a linear trend and ARMA errors,
letting users explore how different model choices affect fit. You can set the true data-generating process,
fit ARMA(p, q) models, and evaluate performance through plots and residual diagnostics.
A good model yields residuals with no visible pattern. The app supports experimenting with overfitting,
underfitting, and sample size, while displaying estimated coefficients and stationarity checks to better understand ARMA behavior.


